{"tid":233803,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Hidden Agenda負責人被帶上警車　英樂隊被帶上入境處旅遊巴","createTime":"2017-05-07T18:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T19:47:24.000Z","uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a728490aa0c9e500140b991f7c5315b654cbf717","tid":233803,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"九龍牛頭角音樂場地 Hidden Agenda （HA），昨晚再遭政府人員「放蛇」；HA 所在的工業大廈地下出現大批軍裝警員，部份持盾，另有警犬被帶到場。警員稱要拘捕 HA 負責人許仲和，許則要求驗傷，雙方僵持；許最終被帶上警車，由立法會議員譚文豪陪同，而表演的英國樂隊成員則被帶上入境處的旅遊巴。<br />\n<br />\n許及樂隊被帶走後，警方陸續收隊，現場人士亦散去。<br />\n<br />\nHidden Agenda 昨晚邀得英國樂隊 Ttng演出；Hidden Agenda 在官方 facebook 專頁表示，入境處職員到場放蛇後指樂隊簽證有問題，並指 Hidden Agenda 場地負責人涉嫌聘請黑工；其間入境處人員企圖強行帶走許仲和，令其受傷，警方則以接報指「有人打架生事」為由到場。<br />\n<br />\n據現場人士稱，表演結束後有兩名入境署人員表明身份，並要求進入後台，雙方發生爭執，隨後有大批警員到場，要求HA人員讓開予入境處「執行職務」。期間，有警員試圖將許仲和帶上警車，雙方爭執期間許仲和坐在地上拒絕離開，警方則稱將會召救護車到場，並問他是否願意到醫院，否則會將他帶返警署。<br />\n<br />\nHidden Agenda是著名本地音樂表演場地，多次被逼遷。上年年底於牛頭角鴻圖道重開。今年三月，曾有食物環境衛生署人員突擊檢查 HA，有食環人員更放蛇購票，並指有需要「搜証」，署方作出口頭警告，又指不排除檢控HA，期間多名警員到場。<br />\n<br />\n來源： <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0hidden-agenda-%E6%94%BE%E8%9B%87-%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E6%8C%81%E7%9B%BE%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E6%AC%B2%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-ha-%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0hidden-agenda-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%259B%2587-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%259B%25BE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AC%25B2%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-ha-%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=85e8764f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0hidden-agenda-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%259B%2587-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%259B%25BE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AC%25B2%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-ha-%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=138974c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0hidden-agenda-%E6%94%BE%E8%9B%87-%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E6%8C%81%E7%9B%BE%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E6%AC%B2%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-ha-%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"2ebfd1fb549a2dcc252f02609a275dc6c868280b","tid":233803,"uid":45238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:57:58.000Z","msg":"咩事"},{"pid":"56c98b554524d64d1c8473ef7a3719b7f415ed33","tid":233803,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:36:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 乜撚野黑工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac51197f5eaa82c95223d2ffeadd5b2aaa117e6","tid":233803,"uid":52473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:36:49.000Z","msg":"唉。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26e975fa368e528afe87e3a4beb94b47ceb7497","tid":233803,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"如果班樂隊有收錢 而佢地又用旅遊簽證黎香港就仆街"},{"pid":"8ead35e031a5972bb995c020c3fdb5e65266e572","tid":233803,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果班樂隊有收錢 而佢地又用旅遊簽證黎香港就仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知最後會點"}]}